      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions for bench-top validation replicate ISO 14879-1 physiological loading (3× body weight axial, 10 Nm torsion, 15° flexion). Temperature, humidity, and specimen preparation documented per ASTM F2083. Boundary conditions in FEA model directly mapped to measured experimental constraints; deviations less than 2% in applied force magnitude."
