      "rationale": "Primary QOIs — peak von Mises stress in tibial tray and bone-implant interface micromotion — are directly linked to clinical failure modes (fatigue fracture and aseptic loosening) documented in FDA MAUDE database and published TKA retrieval studies. QOI traceability matrix maps each computational output to a specific regulatory acceptance criterion and clinical risk."
