      "rationale": "Linear elastic constitutive model adopted for CoCr tibial tray (well-established for metallic implants below yield). Cancellous bone modeled as orthotropic linear elastic with density-modulus relationship from Rho et al. (1995). Model form assumptions documented and justified against published biomechanics literature. Nonlinear geometric effects assessed via sensitivity study; contribution <2% at physiological loads, supporting linear assumption."
